'''Aaron''' was a [[Miaphysite]] [[Coptic Saints|Coptic saint]]. His apocryphal legend says of him, "When he was sick, he made roasted pigeons fly into his mouth." He has a feast in the [[Copt]]ic [[Calendar of saints]] on May 16.
